(1, 'Terms and Conditions', 'content', '<p><strong>Welcome to ERP! By using our platform, you agree to the following terms and conditions. Please read them carefully.</strong></p><h3>1. Acceptance of Terms</h3><blockquote><p>By accessing or using our website and services, you agree to comply with these Terms &amp; Conditions and all applicable laws. If you do not agree, please do not use our services.</p></blockquote><h3>2. Services</h3><blockquote><p>ERP provides a platform to connect clients with personal trainers, offering fitness sessions, online and offline training programs, and related services. All services are subject to availability and applicable pricing.</p></blockquote><h3>3. Account Registration</h3><blockquote><ol><li>Users must register and provide accurate information.</li><li>You are responsible for keeping your account credentials confidential.</li><li>Notify ERP immediately of any unauthorized use of your account.</li></ol></blockquote><h3>4. Booking &amp; Payments</h3><blockquote><ol><li>Booking a session confirms your agreement to pay the listed price.</li><li>Payments are final unless otherwise stated in our refund policy.</li><li>Trainers may cancel or reschedule sessions, and clients will be notified promptly.</li></ol></blockquote><h3>5. Refund &amp; Cancellation Policy</h3><blockquote><ol><li>Refunds and cancellations are subject to the specific package or session purchased.</li><li>Promotional or discounted sessions may be non-refundable.</li></ol></blockquote><h3>6. User Conduct</h3><blockquote><ol><li>Users must not use the platform for unlawful purposes.</li><li>Harassment, abuse, or offensive behavior toward trainers or other users is strictly prohibited.</li><li>Sharing content that infringes intellectual property rights is forbidden.</li></ol></blockquote><h3>7. Intellectual Property</h3><blockquote><ol><li>All content, logos, designs, and software on this platform are owned by ERP or its licensors.</li><li>You may not reproduce, distribute, or modify any part of the platform without permission.</li></ol></blockquote><h3>8. Limitation of Liability</h3><blockquote><ol><li>ERP is not responsible for any injury, loss, or damages resulting from the use of our services.</li><li>Personal training advice is for informational purposes only and does not replace professional medical advice.</li></ol></blockquote><h3>9. Privacy Policy</h3><blockquote><ol><li>Your personal information is handled according to our Privacy Policy.</li><li>By using the platform, you consent to the collection and use of your data as described in the Privacy Policy.</li></ol></blockquote><h3>10. Modifications to Terms</h3><blockquote><ol><li>ERP may update these Terms &amp; Conditions from time to time.</li><li>Changes will be posted on the platform with the updated effective date.</li></ol></blockquote><h3>11. Governing Law</h3><blockquote><ol><li>These Terms &amp; Conditions are governed by the laws of Odisha, without regard to its conflict of laws principles.</li></ol></blockquote>', NULL, 1, 1, 0, '2025-09-12 09:39:23', '2025-10-30 11:21:47');

